description: Sunlight splashes through this breathtaking open space in a professionally managed building with enormous windows capturing views of the Boston skyline. Exposed brick and stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, large closets and a private storage unit in building! Both bedrooms are a good size and condo offers a spa-like bathroom for utmost relaxation. Stunning views from the newly redone large common roofdeck, your perfect spot for July 4th fireworks and St. Patrick's Day! Coin-op Washer/Dryer located in building and there is also a Wash Dry Fold service next door!  This location cannot be beat, right in the heart of Southie, across the street from great restaurants and around the corner from CVS, Lincoln, Loco and Capo! Public Bus route is right outside your door and condo is in close proximity to Dorchester Heights park, and of course the beach! Condo fee includes water, master insurance, common heat, and snow removal. Entire roof replaced in 2022 and after a new roofdeck!
